The paper discusses research in natural language processing, machine learning, knowledge representation, databases, and journalism related to automated fact checking. Based on this, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which focuses on natural language processing and related areas. Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DB (Databases), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
